{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://github.com/mcp-tool-shop-org/backprop-trace/schemas/receipt.v0.5.0.json",
  "title": "backprop-trace canonical receipt schema v0.5.0",
  "description": "v0.9.1 Adam + AdamW optimizer extension. FORCED bump over receipt.v0.4.0 because Update.optimizer.name was a closed enum ['sgd'] and Update.optimizer had additionalProperties:false — additive evolution required widening the enum to ['sgd','adam','adamw'] and adding optional state_before / state_after blocks per-update plus an optional top-level optimizer_config block carrying global hyperparameters (beta1, beta2, epsilon, weight_decay, t). v0.4.0 SGD receipts continue to validate against v0.4.0 schema unchanged (byte-equal preservation); v0.9.1 Adam/AdamW receipts declare schema_version: '0.5.0'. NO per-sample gradients in batched receipts (deferred). NO momentum SGD (v0.9.2). NO Nesterov / AMSGrad / per-parameter-groups / LR schedules / gradient clipping / mixed precision (deferred). Trust framing: Adam-rules (22, 23, 24) verify structural consistency of recorded (g, m, v, t, update); they do NOT prove the gradient came from a real trainer or real data. An attacker who controls every byte of the sidecar and recomputes a consistent (g, m, v, update) quadruple passes Rules 22-24 trivially — analogous to the Rule 17 bundle-integrity caveat and to the Fang et al. 2023 spoofing class against Proof-of-Learning. For producer-identity binding, combine with Rule 16 (attestor.signed_subject_digest), Sigstore / cosign signature, or out-of-band attestation.",
  "type": "object",
  "x-changes-from-v0.4.0": [
    "schema_version const bumped 0.4.0 -> 0.5.0",
    "NEW optional top-level optimizer_config block: when authoring_state and optimizer name are adam/adamw, declares global hyperparameters (name, learning_rate, beta1, beta2, epsilon, weight_decay?, t). SGD receipts MAY omit optimizer_config (the top-level learning_rate field already carries lr); Adam/AdamW receipts MUST include it (enforced by allOf conditional).",
    "Update.optimizer.name enum widened: ['sgd'] -> ['sgd', 'adam', 'adamw']. SGD-only receipts under v0.4.0 schema retain exact byte shape; Adam/AdamW receipts declare schema_version: '0.5.0' and use the wider enum.",
    "Update.optimizer gains optional state_before + state_after blocks. For Adam/AdamW these carry per-parameter (m, v) state; for SGD they MUST be omitted (preserves SGD byte-equality with v0.4.0).",
    "When Update.optimizer.name in {adam, adamw}, state_before and state_after are REQUIRED (allOf conditional inside Update).",
    "When optimizer_config.name in {adam, adamw}, beta1/beta2/epsilon/t are REQUIRED on optimizer_config (allOf conditional at the top level).",
    "When optimizer_config.name === 'adamw', weight_decay is REQUIRED on optimizer_config (allOf conditional at the top level).",
    "NO removed fields. NO renamed fields. NO breaking changes to existing v0.4.0 SGD receipt shape. v0.4.0 SGD receipts validate against v0.4.0 schema unchanged. v0.9.1 Adam/AdamW receipts declare schema_version: '0.5.0' and pick up the new conditional requirements."
  ],
  "x-order": [
    "schema_version",
    "fixture",
    "step",
    "fixture_status",
    "source_framework",
    "attestor",
    "metadata",
    "numeric_policy",
    "bias_policy",
    "topology",
    "learning_rate",
    "optimizer_config",
    "trace_id",
    "step_index",
    "batch",
    "inputs",
    "targets",
    "parameters_before",
    "per_sample",
    "forward",
    "loss",
    "backward",
    "updates",
    "parameters_after",
    "post_update_forward",
    "post_update_loss"
  ],
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "required": [
    "schema_version",
    "fixture",
    "step",
    "fixture_status",
    "numeric_policy",
    "bias_policy",
    "topology",
    "learning_rate",
    "inputs",
    "targets",
    "parameters_before",
    "forward",
    "loss",
    "backward",
    "updates",
    "parameters_after"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "schema_version": { "const": "0.5.0" },
    "fixture": { "type": "string" },
    "step": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1 },
    "fixture_status": { "$ref": "#/$defs/FixtureStatus" },
    "source_framework": {
      "description": "OPTIONAL. REQUIRED at the reconciler boundary (Rule 0 sub-check) when fixture_status.authoring_state === 'external_imported'. Same shape as v0.4.0.",
      "$ref": "#/$defs/SourceFramework"
    },
    "attestor": {
      "description": "OPTIONAL. REQUIRED at the reconciler boundary when fixture_status.authoring_state === 'external_imported'. Same shape as v0.4.0.",
      "$ref": "#/$defs/Attestor"
    },
    "metadata": { "type": "object" },
    "numeric_policy": { "$ref": "#/$defs/NumericPolicy" },
    "bias_policy": { "$ref": "#/$defs/BiasPolicy" },
    "topology": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Topology" },
    "learning_rate": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
    "optimizer_config": {
      "description": "OPTIONAL. REQUIRED at the reconciler boundary when any update.optimizer.name is in {adam, adamw}. SGD-only receipts MAY omit this block (the top-level learning_rate field carries lr). When present, declares global optimizer hyperparameters and the step counter t (for Adam bias correction). Rules 20 (shape consistency), 22 (moment recurrences), 23 (bias correction), 24 (parameter update), and 26 (config constancy across multi-step) consume these values. v0.9.1 supports sgd / adam / adamw only; momentum SGD is v0.9.2; Nesterov / AMSGrad / per-parameter-groups deferred.",
      "$ref": "#/$defs/OptimizerConfig"
    },
    "trace_id": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[0-9a-f]{32}$" },
    "step_index": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0 },
    "batch": {
      "description": "OPTIONAL (v0.9+). Same shape as v0.4.0. v0.9.1 supports batched Adam/AdamW: per-sample state is NOT carried (reduced m/v only at top-level updates[].optimizer.state_*). Per-sample optimizer state deferred to v0.9.x/v0.10 alongside per-sample gradients.",
      "$ref": "#/$defs/Batch"
    },
    "inputs": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitNumberMap" },
    "targets": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitNumberMap" },
    "parameters_before": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ParameterMap" },
    "per_sample": {
      "description": "OPTIONAL (v0.9+, REQUIRED at the reconciler boundary when batch.size > 1). Same shape as v0.4.0.",
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": {
        "type": "object",
        "additionalProperties": false,
        "required": ["inputs", "targets", "forward", "loss"],
        "properties": {
          "inputs": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitNumberMap" },
          "targets": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitNumberMap" },
          "forward": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ForwardMap" },
          "loss": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Loss" }
        }
      }
    },
    "forward": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ForwardMap" },
    "loss": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Loss" },
    "backward": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Backward" },
    "updates": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Update" }
    },
    "parameters_after": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ParameterMap" },
    "post_update_forward": { "$ref": "#/$defs/PostUpdateForward" },
    "post_update_loss": { "$ref": "#/$defs/PostUpdateLoss" }
  },
  "allOf": [
    {
      "x-purpose": "Co-presence guard: trace_id and step_index. Same as v0.4.0.",
      "anyOf": [
        { "not": { "required": ["step_index"] } },
        { "required": ["trace_id"] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "x-purpose": "Co-presence guard inverse: trace_id requires step_index. Same as v0.4.0.",
      "anyOf": [
        { "not": { "required": ["trace_id"] } },
        { "required": ["step_index"] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "x-purpose": "v0.9.1 NEW: when optimizer_config.name is adam or adamw, beta1/beta2/epsilon/t are required.",
      "type": "object",
      "if": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["optimizer_config"],
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": {
              "name": { "enum": ["adam", "adamw"] }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "then": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "beta1", "beta2", "epsilon", "t"]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "x-purpose": "v0.9.1 NEW: when optimizer_config.name is adamw, weight_decay is also required.",
      "type": "object",
      "if": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["optimizer_config"],
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": {
              "name": { "const": "adamw" }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "then": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "beta1", "beta2", "epsilon", "t", "weight_decay"]
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "$defs": {
    "UnitOrder": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["input", "hidden", "output"],
      "properties": {
        "input": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" } },
        "hidden": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" } },
        "output": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" } }
      }
    },
    "ParameterOrder": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "uniqueItems": true,
      "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" }
    },
    "FixtureStatus": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["authoring_state", "verification_state", "canonical", "promote_to", "describes_in", "blockers_to_promotion"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["authoring_state", "verification_state", "canonical"],
      "properties": {
        "authoring_state": {
          "enum": ["hand_derived", "engine_generated", "engine_generated_general", "deliberately_corrupted", "external_imported"]
        },
        "verification_state": {
          "enum": ["pending_engine_reproduction", "engine_reproduced_byte_equal", "expected_to_fail_reconciliation", "engine_recompute_matched_within_tolerance", "engine_recompute_disagreed", "engine_recompute_skipped_with_basis"]
        },
        "canonical": { "type": "boolean" },
        "promote_to": { "type": "string" },
        "describes_in": { "type": "string" },
        "blockers_to_promotion": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } }
      }
    },
    "SourceFramework": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["name", "version", "information_uri", "extractor"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["name", "version"],
      "properties": {
        "name": { "enum": ["pytorch", "jax", "tensorflow", "hand_derived", "backprop_trace_engine"] },
        "version": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
        "information_uri": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
        "extractor": {
          "type": "object",
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "required": ["name", "version"],
          "properties": {
            "name": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
            "version": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Attestor": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["computed_by", "verified_by", "differential_tolerance", "import_provenance", "skip_basis", "signed_subject_digest", "bundle_root_digest"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["computed_by", "verified_by", "differential_tolerance"],
      "properties": {
        "computed_by": { "$ref": "#/$defs/AttestorIdentity" },
        "verified_by": { "$ref": "#/$defs/AttestorIdentity" },
        "differential_tolerance": {
          "type": "object",
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "required": ["atol", "rtol"],
          "properties": {
            "atol": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 },
            "rtol": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 }
          }
        },
        "import_provenance": {
          "type": "object",
          "x-order": ["source_format", "source_hash", "import_timestamp"],
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "required": ["source_format", "source_hash"],
          "properties": {
            "source_format": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
            "source_hash": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^sha256:[0-9a-f]{64}$" },
            "import_timestamp": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 }
          }
        },
        "skip_basis": {
          "enum": ["hardware_nondeterminism", "framework_op_unsupported", "distributed_only_field", "attested_third_party"]
        },
        "signed_subject_digest": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^sha256:[0-9a-f]{64}$" },
        "bundle_root_digest": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^sha256:[0-9a-f]{64}$" }
      }
    },
    "AttestorIdentity": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["kind", "identity"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["kind", "identity"],
      "properties": {
        "kind": { "enum": ["framework", "engine", "hand_derivation"] },
        "identity": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 }
      }
    },
    "OptimizerConfig": {
      "description": "v0.9.1 — global optimizer hyperparameters + step counter. Per-receipt scope (each multi-step receipt declares its own t and lr, allowing LR schedules across steps). beta1/beta2/epsilon/t conditionally required when name in {adam, adamw}; weight_decay conditionally required when name === adamw. Closed enum on name preserves additive evolution discipline.",
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["name", "learning_rate", "beta1", "beta2", "epsilon", "weight_decay", "t"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["name", "learning_rate"],
      "properties": {
        "name": { "enum": ["sgd", "adam", "adamw"] },
        "learning_rate": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
        "beta1": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0, "exclusiveMaximum": 1 },
        "beta2": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0, "exclusiveMaximum": 1 },
        "epsilon": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
        "weight_decay": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 },
        "t": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1 }
      }
    },
    "AdamState": {
      "description": "v0.9.1 — per-parameter Adam/AdamW state (m, v). Canonical names match Kingma & Ba 2014 Algorithm 1 directly: m = first moment estimate (signed), v = second moment estimate (non-negative). Framework importers normalize from PyTorch (exp_avg → m, exp_avg_sq → v), optax (mu → m, nu → v), TF Keras (Adam/m/<param> → m, Adam/v/<param> → v). Bias-corrected m_hat = m/(1-beta1^t) and v_hat = v/(1-beta2^t) are DERIVED, NEVER stored — Rule 23 recomputes them at verify time from (state_after, beta1, beta2, t).",
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["m", "v"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["m", "v"],
      "properties": {
        "m": { "type": "number" },
        "v": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 }
      }
    },
    "NumericPolicy": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["number_encoding", "precision_significant_digits", "rounding", "tolerance", "computation_order", "byte_output"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["number_encoding", "precision_significant_digits", "rounding", "tolerance"],
      "properties": {
        "number_encoding": { "const": "decimal" },
        "precision_significant_digits": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1 },
        "rounding": { "const": "round_half_to_even" },
        "tolerance": {
          "oneOf": [
            {
              "type": "object", "required": ["atol", "rtol"], "additionalProperties": false,
              "properties": { "atol": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 }, "rtol": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 } }
            },
            { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 }
          ]
        },
        "computation_order": { "const": "schema_defined" },
        "byte_output": {
          "type": "object",
          "x-order": ["format", "json_key_order", "trailing_zero_policy", "indent"],
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "properties": {
            "format": { "const": "jsonl" },
            "json_key_order": { "const": "schema_defined" },
            "trailing_zero_policy": { "const": "pad_to_significant_digits" },
            "indent": { "const": "none" }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "BiasPolicy": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["mode", "reason", "updated_in_step", "reconciliation"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["mode", "updated_in_step"],
      "properties": {
        "mode": { "enum": ["constant", "sgd"] },
        "reason": { "type": "string" },
        "updated_in_step": { "type": "boolean" },
        "reconciliation": { "type": "string" }
      }
    },
    "Topology": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["layers", "input_size", "hidden_size", "output_size", "unit_order", "parameter_order", "parameters", "activation_hidden", "activation_output", "loss", "bias_sharing"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["layers", "input_size", "hidden_size", "output_size", "unit_order", "parameter_order", "parameters", "activation_hidden", "activation_output", "loss", "bias_sharing"],
      "properties": {
        "layers": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "input_size": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 64 },
        "hidden_size": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 64 },
        "output_size": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 64 },
        "unit_order": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitOrder" },
        "parameter_order": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ParameterOrder" },
        "parameters": {
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 1,
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["id", "role"],
            "properties": {
              "id": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" },
              "role": { "enum": ["input_to_hidden_weight", "hidden_to_output_weight", "hidden_bias", "output_bias"] },
              "from_unit": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" },
              "to_unit": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" },
              "applies_to_units": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" } }
            }
          }
        },
        "activation_hidden": { "enum": ["sigmoid", "identity", "relu"] },
        "activation_output": { "enum": ["sigmoid", "identity", "relu", "softmax"] },
        "loss": { "enum": ["half_squared_error", "cross_entropy_softmax"] },
        "bias_sharing": { "enum": ["per_layer", "per_neuron"] }
      }
    },
    "UnitNumberMap": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
    "ParameterMap": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
    "ForwardMap": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ForwardUnit" } },
    "ForwardUnit": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["net", "out"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["net", "out"],
      "properties": { "net": { "type": "number" }, "out": { "type": "number" } }
    },
    "Batch": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["size", "sample_order", "reduction"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["size", "sample_order", "reduction"],
      "properties": {
        "size": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1 },
        "sample_order": {
          "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "uniqueItems": true,
          "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" }
        },
        "reduction": { "enum": ["mean", "sum", "none"] }
      }
    },
    "Loss": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["per_output", "per_sample", "reduction", "total"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["per_output", "total"],
      "properties": {
        "per_output": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
        "per_sample": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
        "reduction": { "enum": ["mean", "sum", "none"] },
        "total": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "Backward": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["output_error_signals", "hidden_error_signals"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["output_error_signals", "hidden_error_signals"],
      "properties": {
        "output_error_signals": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/$defs/OutputErrorSignal" } },
        "hidden_error_signals": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/$defs/HiddenErrorSignal" } }
      }
    },
    "OutputErrorSignal": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["factors", "product_order", "signal_value", "dual_form"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["factors", "product_order", "signal_value"],
      "properties": {
        "factors": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/NamedFactor" } },
        "product_order": { "const": "left_to_right" },
        "signal_value": { "type": "number" },
        "dual_form": { "$ref": "#/$defs/DualForm" }
      }
    },
    "DualForm": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["jacobian_terms", "product_order", "summation_order", "summed_value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["jacobian_terms", "product_order", "summation_order", "summed_value"],
      "properties": {
        "jacobian_terms": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/JacobianTerm" } },
        "product_order": { "const": "left_to_right" },
        "summation_order": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "summed_value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "JacobianTerm": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["target_unit", "factors", "term_value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["target_unit", "factors", "term_value"],
      "properties": {
        "target_unit": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" },
        "factors": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/NamedFactor" } },
        "term_value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "HiddenErrorSignal": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["downstream_contributions", "summation_order", "backpropagated_sum", "activation_derivative", "product_order", "signal_value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["downstream_contributions", "summation_order", "backpropagated_sum", "activation_derivative", "product_order", "signal_value"],
      "properties": {
        "downstream_contributions": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/DownstreamContribution" } },
        "summation_order": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "backpropagated_sum": { "type": "number" },
        "activation_derivative": { "type": "number" },
        "product_order": { "const": "left_to_right" },
        "signal_value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "DownstreamContribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["from", "downstream_signal", "via_weight", "weight_value", "value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["from", "downstream_signal", "via_weight", "weight_value", "value"],
      "properties": {
        "from": { "type": "string" },
        "downstream_signal": { "type": "number" },
        "via_weight": { "type": "string" },
        "weight_value": { "type": "number" },
        "value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "NamedFactor": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["name", "from", "value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["name", "value"],
      "properties": {
        "name": { "type": "string" },
        "from": { "type": "string" },
        "value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "Update": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["parameter_id", "kind", "layer_edge", "parameter_role", "from_unit", "to_unit", "weight_before", "optimizer", "gradient", "update", "weight_after"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["parameter_id", "kind", "weight_before", "optimizer", "gradient", "update", "weight_after"],
      "properties": {
        "parameter_id": { "type": "string" },
        "kind": { "enum": ["weight", "bias"] },
        "layer_edge": { "enum": ["input_to_hidden", "hidden_to_output", "bias_to_layer"] },
        "parameter_role": { "type": "string" },
        "from_unit": { "type": "string" },
        "to_unit": { "type": "string" },
        "weight_before": { "type": "number" },
        "optimizer": {
          "type": "object",
          "x-order": ["name", "learning_rate", "factors", "product_order", "state_before", "state_after"],
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "factors", "product_order"],
          "properties": {
            "name": { "enum": ["sgd", "adam", "adamw"] },
            "learning_rate": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
            "factors": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/NamedFactor" } },
            "product_order": { "const": "left_to_right" },
            "state_before": { "$ref": "#/$defs/AdamState" },
            "state_after": { "$ref": "#/$defs/AdamState" }
          }
        },
        "gradient": { "type": "number" },
        "update": { "type": "number" },
        "weight_after": { "type": "number" }
      },
      "allOf": [
        {
          "x-purpose": "v0.9.1 NEW: when this update's optimizer.name is adam or adamw, state_before and state_after are REQUIRED on optimizer.",
          "type": "object",
          "if": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["optimizer"],
            "properties": {
              "optimizer": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name"],
                "properties": { "name": { "enum": ["adam", "adamw"] } }
              }
            }
          },
          "then": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "optimizer": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "factors", "product_order", "state_before", "state_after"]
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "PostUpdateForward": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["status"],
      "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ForwardUnit" },
      "properties": {
        "status": { "enum": ["pending_engine_first_run", "filled"] },
        "required_before_promotion": { "type": "boolean" },
        "fields_required": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "fill_specification": { "type": "string" },
        "note": { "type": "string" }
      }
    },
    "PostUpdateLoss": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["status", "required_before_promotion", "fields_required", "drift_check_against_published", "note", "per_output", "total"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["status"],
      "properties": {
        "status": { "enum": ["pending_engine_first_run", "filled"] },
        "required_before_promotion": { "type": "boolean" },
        "fields_required": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "drift_check_against_published": { "type": "object" },
        "note": { "type": "string" },
        "per_output": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
        "total": { "type": "number" }
      }
    }
  }
}
